creator: The Recovery Tribe, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
WHY R|TRIBE? Live connected! Feel better! Hope, Healing, & Help - No matter your circumstance. Timely professional support is available to help you change your life and improve your connection with your significant other, spouse, loved ones or family. Find your tribe, achieve true healing, reach your goals in a safe and supportive community.

KEY BENEFITS:
Online Support - Accessible, Affordable, Anonymous, & Secure
Expert Counselors and Coaches - For Your Specific Needs
Messaging and Video Options - Choice! Try for Free!
Community - Join or Create Peer Support Groups.

WHAT IS R|TRIBE?
rTribe is the first counseling and habit change platform to offer an innovative smart-match solution (via our proprietary TribeMatch™ technology) to the best licensed therapists and certified coaches combined with world-class peer support, accountability and analytic insights. Finally, people can find affordable, ‘just in time’ support and experience deep transformation. rTribe connects people with themselves, their purpose, community, and professional care.

rTribe empowers you to have secure, confidential, vulnerable and authentic conversations with counselors, coaches, and peers, turning personal struggles into strengths. Find the honesty, courage, and support you need to thrive!

HOW DOES R|TRIBE WORK?
It’s never been easier to get professional help. Within minutes, you can instantly be TribeMatched to the ideal licensed coach for your specific needs. Start with a “worry-free” 3-day trial securely connecting you via unlimited messaging and scheduled live video/voice sessions.

IS ONLINE COACHING EFFECTIVE?
Studies confirm the effectiveness of the online medium for making life changes. Tracking your progress through rTribe, sharing that with your friends, and getting support from your provider is a powerful combination to experience deep change.

It will require courage and commitment. By connecting with a safe professional who has the knowledge, care, and skills to help; you can finally find true healing and hope.

HOW MUCH DOES IT COST?
rTribe offers unlimited access to licensed professionals at a fraction of the cost of traditional support. There are no contracts whatsoever and you can cancel anytime.

Plans Offered (billed monthly):

Chat Sessions $37.50/week:
Unlimited chat
1 Daily provider check-in

Chat & video counseling $49.25/week:
Unlimited chat
1 Daily provider check-in
1 Live 30-minute session per month

Premium Chat and Video Counseling $99/week
Unlimited chat
2 Daily provider check-ins
4 Live 30-minute sessions per month


WHO ARE THE PROVIDERS?
Providers on rTribe are independent contractors who’ve been screened to provide an exceptional quality of care. Providers are generally certified coaches. Licensed therapists may work as a coach.

IS R|TRIBE SECURE AND CONFIDENTIAL?
Yes! Your privacy and safety are the top priority for us. We use military/bank-grade encryption. Also, you can be completely anonymous. Your provider is committed to maintaining your privacy and confidentiality.


PREMIUM FEATURES
Everyone starts a 30-day free trial of our premium subscription. If you decide to subscribe, the service automatically renews and costs $5.99/month or $59.99/year (that’s 2 free months!). Subscriptions may be managed by you and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to your Play Store -> Account after purchase.

Premium features, you will get access to:
• Track your and your friends’ detailed progress.
• Set your privacy level.
• Keep mentors and recovery guides up to date on your progress via weekly emails.

WE ARE HERE FOR YOU!
- Provider Support Email - providersupport@rtribe.org
- Provider Application - https://www.rtribe.org/become-a-counselor/

Description

Four Streams Coaching™ was built on the simple belief that every person has value. We strive to help everyone realize their fullest potential by partnering with them to reveal what truly is extraordinary about them. We work with clients globally to envision, work towards, and accomplish their most meaningful goals. This transformational model is much different than traditional coaching, which focuses on actions and results and stays very surface level. Four Streams Coaches™ come along side each client to instill deep sustainable change that's worthwhile with the combination of tools from our four disciplines: our world-class Coaching Methodology, Neuroscience, Positive Psychology, and Worldview.

In an effort to make the 4S Talent Growth app experience the best possible, we made several enhancements, adjustments, and tweaks to ensure a seamless experience.
Also, we’re excited to announce that this release introduces an incredibly powerful framework to help you grow via our proprietary PERMA + Health quiz! This scientifically-based free quiz enables you to identify which area of well-being you should focus on to build actionable growth-focused habits and acknowledge challenging obstacles in order to experience lasting sustainable change.
Additionally, this update brings you an enhanced check-in page that integrates habit tracking and progressive growth which you can opt to share with others. We have also created an all new Growth Pathway Insights page that allows you to track your progress! Happy growing!


Description

Mired in a stagnant routine that isn’t producing the results that you’d like? Feeling aimless, directionless, or generally unfulfilled? Have lofty goals but no actionable plan to attain them?
We believe that healthy relationships must be mutually beneficial. Organizations, who invest in the professional as well as personal well-being of their talent, create a substantial competitive advantage over their competitors. Consequently, we have created a proprietary 4/S Talent Growth app designed specifically to help individuals thrive both professionally and personally.
By using scientifically-proven personal assessments, quizzes, goal identifiers with progress tracking, and world-class coaches; our app provides everything you need to live a more meaningful rewarding life. With daily actionable items, we deliver tailor-made opportunities to achieve long-term results one step at a time.

Description

R|Tribe is a company that offers people-focused integrated software + on-demand consulting solutions. Our first product offering is "Four Streams."

For over a decade, we have developed and implemented our scientifically-driven methodology in corporate environments. The Four Streams methodology has been successfully implemented in organizations of all sizes, using our assessment tools + our highly specialized Personal Growth Consultants to bring work-life balance to the members of an organization.

Four Streams provides leadership with a data-informed integrated approach to hiring, retaining, and growing talent. For current talent and potential hires, we provide tools that enable:

• Understanding via a unique identity profile
• Insights via a growth awareness evaluation
• Action via development of a personal growth journey

Every step of a person’s journey is supported through 24/7 access to on-demand Growth Consultants. The result -- highly engaged and aligned talent that produces a flourishing and successful organization.
